20:02.701 --> 20:05.621
<i>billing all of these hours</i>
<i>above an unpaid retainer</i>

20:05.704 --> 20:10.083
<i>at $1,000 an hour,</i>
<i>were you ever able to get Anna</i>

20:10.167 --> 20:13.170
<i>close to getting a loan approved</i>
<i>or transferred to her custody?</i>

20:13.253 --> 20:14.546
<i>No.</i>

20:14.630 --> 20:18.091
