21:15.565 --> 21:16.858
Unfortunately.

21:17.609 --> 21:19.695
Did you tell her you wanted to kiss her?

21:19.778 --> 21:21.738
-Objection.
-Sustained.

21:24.032 --> 21:25.784
Yeah, you definitely did.

21:31.540 --> 21:35.252
A courtroom is an unexpected
venue for a fashion show,

21:35.335 --> 21:37.796
but everything about Anna Delvey,

21:37.879 --> 21:40.424
the fake German heiress
on trial in Manhattan,

21:40.507 --> 21:42.592
seems to surprise and fascinate.

21:42.676 --> 21:46.263
<i>Now Anna Delvey's courtroom wardrobe</i>
<i>has its own Instagram account.</i>

21:46.346 --> 21:48.682
<i>Who created the account? No one knows.</i>

21:48.765 --> 21:51.768
<i>But Anna's iconic outfits</i>
<i>are now must-have fashion,</i>

21:51.852 --> 21:53.812
<i>and it's all due to a celebrity stylist.</i>

21:54.521 --> 21:55.856
I know this is you.

21:55.939 --> 21:58.108
Your fingerprints
are all over this hashtag.

21:58.191 --> 22:02.571
Kacy, don't accuse me of doing
something I'm damn proud of doing.

22:02.654 --> 22:06.283
What you're doing is making it
so this poor girl has to tell her sad-ass,

22:06.366 --> 22:10.662
embarrassing story to the entire world
instead of just a jury.

22:10.746 --> 22:12.998
Anna could go to prison for 15 years,

22:13.081 --> 22:16.043
and you're worried
about Becky's 15 minutes of shame.

22:16.126 --> 22:18.337
-Stop calling me Becky.
-Okay, Karen.

22:18.420 --> 22:23.175
When are you going to wake the fuck up
and realize you're Satan's secretary?

22:23.258 --> 22:24.968
At her beck and call 24/7.

22:25.052 --> 22:26.136
Damn straight.

22:26.219 --> 22:29.306
