to run a defense for a trial.

22:40.150 --> 22:44.071
So every day she hustles,
trades Cup Noodles,

22:44.154 --> 22:45.822
instant coffee, fucking tampons,

22:45.906 --> 22:48.658
whatever she can get her hands on
through the commissary

22:48.742 --> 22:50.994
