24:49.863 --> 24:52.073
Everyone's going
to hate me after I testify.

24:52.908 --> 24:54.618
Will you hate you?

24:56.995 --> 24:58.413
Stand in your truth,

24:58.497 --> 25:02.000
fortified by kindness,
and tell your story…

25:03.543 --> 25:04.836
you bad bitch.

25:12.719 --> 25:15.263
Miss McCaw, I'm not getting any younger.

25:16.181 --> 25:19.392
-The people call Rachel Deloache Williams.

25:19.476 --> 25:21.978
D-E-L-O-A-C-H-E.

25:22.062 --> 25:23.271
Thank you.

25:23.355 --> 25:24.481
And welcome.

25:27.025 --> 25:28.568
Yes, thank you.

25:28.652 --> 25:30.570
I know this hasn't been
an easy time for you.

25:31.238 --> 25:33.490
-Where do you live, Rachel?
-The West Village.

25:33.573 --> 25:36.076
-Where did you go to college?
-Kenyon College.

25:36.159 --> 25:37.619
Why did you come to New York?

25:37.702 --> 25:40.956
I wanted to become a writer.
And to work at <i>Vanity Fair.</i>

25:41.039 --> 25:42.791
-And did you?
-I did.

25:43.500 --> 25:46.878
How long did it take to obtain
a position there after arriving here?

25:46.962 --> 25:49.256
-Three months.
-And could you tell us how?

25:49.339 --> 25:52.425
I got an informational interview
with a woman who worked there

25:52.509 --> 25:55.637
and we seemed to hit it off,
but I didn't hear back so…

25:56.346 --> 25:59.516
I sent a hand-written
forget-me-not note with,

25:59.599 --> 26:02.310
like, this book of kind of dorky poems

26:02.394 --> 26:04.854
and a box of tea
asking her to keep me in mind.

26:05.730 --> 26:09.192
I went in and interviewed
the next day and started the day after.

26:14.072 --> 26:18.285
Miss Williams, before we go down
the rabbit-hole of your horrible hardship

26:18.368 --> 26:21.204
and struggle in your attempt
to be reimbursed by Miss Sorokin,

26:21.288 --> 26:23.039
I was hoping you'd tell the court

26:23.123 --> 26:25.292
how this experience
has affected your life.

26:25.375 --> 26:27.627
My life? Sure.

26:29.296 --> 26:32.966
Honestly, the money,
the stress she caused me with my work,

26:33.049 --> 26:35.594
and family, as horrible as all that was,

26:35.677 --> 26:38.263
