it will all pass eventually, but--

26:38.346 --> 26:39.556
But…

26:39.639 --> 26:42.142
you were close with the defendant.

26:44.144 --> 26:45.020
Yes.

26:45.103 --> 26:48.356
Is that why you trusted her,
defended her, helped her even when--

26:48.440 --> 26:49.441
I loved Anna.

26:50.650 --> 26:51.860
