to trust will ever change.

27:33.360 --> 27:38.782
If I'll ever be myself again.
If I'll ever be able to let someone in.

27:39.866 --> 27:41.117
To love.

27:47.248 --> 27:48.249
Do you need a moment?

27:52.837 --> 27:54.255
I'm so sorry.

27:57.092 --> 27:58.093
I'm sorry.

27:59.969 --> 28:00.887
I'm okay.

28:02.180 --> 28:05.433
I'm okay. I'm okay. Please.

28:07.435 --> 28:12.941
