29:26.347 --> 29:27.182
Um…

29:34.647 --> 29:36.441
But I'm calling to see

29:36.524 --> 29:39.235
if you've reconsidered
joining us in person.

29:44.073 --> 29:45.950
-<i>Nyet.</i>
-He says no.

29:46.034 --> 29:47.285
I got that.

29:48.119 --> 29:52.749
So Vadim, the thing is,
your daughter is a little distraught.

29:53.750 --> 29:55.877
Which isn't to say we're losing,
we're not,

29:55.960 --> 29:58.838
but given the stresses
of a trial like this,

29:58.922 --> 30:01.007
especially with all this media attention--

30:09.265 --> 30:12.101
There's really no substitute for family.

30:12.185 --> 30:14.103
She needs her family here.

30:21.778 --> 30:22.779
Please.

30:27.575 --> 30:29.077
Your own daughter?

30:29.160 --> 30:30.995
On trial in a foreign country.

30:31.079 --> 30:33.331
I am just her lawyer, Vadim.

30:34.165 --> 30:35.625
I can't be her father too.

30:35.708 --> 30:36.793
I can't do this.

30:37.418 --> 30:38.962
I can't be everything for her.

30:43.800 --> 30:45.009
